<br>
First of all u can do 6 front spawns solo with no problem as described above simply set up 51 earth pet BO3 DS pull first one (front right) with malosi use 2 vs summoned nukes to outdamage pet. (pet suvives with 50-60%)<br>
<br>
Pull next with a little trick USE the CLAY BRACELET or use your lvl 8 (?) spell eye of zomm which u never used b4 ;-). The one around the corner will aggro eye kill it and come after u then. So he comes to the water where u set up camp. After those two are dead move til u sit between their spawn points, med til pet full. Use malise to pull the one on the left from max distance should come solo sometimes both come (had about 3 times out of like 100 cycles!!) kill it. Wait til pet healed to 90+% pull one on right with malise. The ones behind sometimes about 30% of the time come both, therefore med to full when both come dont panic, send pet on one and nuke it to death use 3 vs summoned nukes maybe 4. Then mabe chain a pet. well done btw respawn timer is 27<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :x --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/sick.gif ALT=":x"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> x minutes i can do one cycle in like 16 minutes when i hurry up so its enough time.<br>
<br>
When u wanna have more fun and help a friend and get better xp do the following:<br>
<br>
get u a friend (i prefer a 41 guild druid ;-) bec of summone nuke.<br>
<br>
DO same as above except druid helps u nuking and maybe root if mobs run ;-).<br>
<br>
After u are done with the 6 in front normally after 10minutes bec u have lots more mana now (the druids mana ;-)). Med to full.<br>
<br>
The the trick how to pull cruscader. Use clay bracelet (quest in solusek ro, very easy) make eye of zomm look arond corner wait til roaming cruscader was there and moves away (important) then fly in turn to left target the warrior, then druid assist u. Once cruscader which is on the right and warrior come druid tries to root warrior b4 he reaches pet. U send pet on cruscader. Then u can both nuke on cruscader and kill him.<br>
Then kill warrior. If root is resistet let the mobs chase u  and pet tank both nuke WARRIOR to death the quickly (bec he has low hp!). then kill cruscader maybe chain a pet while druid roots the cruscader (of course u have to debuff mobs if druid is that low but resist rates arent that high, try it out).<br>
Once u killed them pull roaming cruscader with clay bracer (eye of zomm).<br>
The big advantage on doing it with eye of zomm is u dont have to run so far to zone when anything wents wrong bec u sit right at zone ;-) and those things double for up to 115 if im right warriors for 97.<br>
<br>
The Hp on a warrior are like 2-2.5k on cruscader around 3 but they resist better.<br>
<br>
Hope that helps btw i do around 3/4 of a blue at 53 on one cycle (9 spawns) which leads to around 1,5 blue a h 2 spawns at 27 minutes.<br>
<br>
Fierystorm Phantomwalker 53 Elementalist of Strom der Gezeiten<br>
